next.excerpt:
Today we're finally playing Minecraft for the first time!
New Episodes drop on Thursdays and Sundays @ 12:00 PM EST

🌟 Socials 🌟
📺 Watch me live at: http://www.twitch.tv/sypherpk 
🐥 Twitter: http://www.twitter.com/sypherpk 
📷 Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/sypherpk/ 
💌 Discord: https://discordapp.com/invite/sypherpk
📚 Facebook: https://facebook.com/SypherPK

🎥 Produced, Edited and Thumbnail by: JackZenn: 
https://twitter.com/JackMelaschenko 

Hey everyone it’s SypherPK, and welcome back to my Minecraft Let's Play! I try to keep these videos as clean and family friendly as possible. Today it's my first time EVER playing Minecraft! I have never played the game before so this is my first attempts at making tools and surviving my first night. Hope you enjoy! 

#Minecraft #sypherplays #sypherpk
